text: Elati (), may refer to several villages and a mountain in Greece: *Elati (mountain), a mountain in the heart of the island of Lefkada *Elati, Arcadia, a settlement in Arcadia *Elati, Arta, a settlement in the Arta regional unit *Elati, Ioannina, a settlement in the Ioannina regional unit *Elati, Kozani, a village in the Kozani regional unit *Elati, Trikala, a village in the Trikala regional unit ==See also== *Elatia (disambiguation)
title: Elati
